# ==============================================================================

# SpectraMind V50 — DVC Ignore Rules (Upgraded, Mission-Grade)

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Purpose:

# • Prevent DVC from scanning/adding ephemeral, environment, or rebuildable files

# • Keep the DVC DAG clean, reproducible, and Kaggle/CI-safe

# • Complements .gitignore — these patterns affect only DVC’s file discovery

#

# Notes:

# • DO NOT ignore real datasets/models that you intend to manage with DVC.

# • Keep dvc.yaml, dvc.lock, and \*.dvc visible to DVC (never ignore them).

# • Prefer storing true datasets under data/ and registering via `dvc add`.

# ==============================================================================

